{"metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"multiPolygonWithPolygons:"}],"roleHeading":"Type Method","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNMultiPolygon(cm)multiPolygonWithPolygons:","title":"multiPolygonWithPolygons:","symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"multiPolygonWithPolygons:"}],"role":"symbol"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Creates and returns a multipolygon object consisting of the given polygons."}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolygon\/multipolygonwithpolygons:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"+ (","kind":"text"},{"text":"instancetype","kind":"keyword"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"text":"multiPolygonWithPolygons:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSArray<MLNPolygon *>","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:Q$objc(cs)NSArray"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"polygons","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"polygons","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The array of polygons defining the shape.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"return-value","level":2,"text":"Return Value","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"A new multipolygon object.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon\/multiPolygonWithPolygons:"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon"]]},"kind":"symbol","references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNPolygon":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolygon","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolygon"},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a closed shape consisting of four or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"vertices, specified as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"type":"text","text":" instances, and the edges that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"connect them. For example, you could use a polygon shape to represent a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"building, a lake, or an area you want to highlight."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNPolygon"}],"title":"MLNPolygon","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnpolygon","type":"topic","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"role":"collection","abstract":[{"text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"MapLibre","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMultiPolygon/multiPolygonWithPolygons:":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolygon\/multipolygonwithpolygons:","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Creates and returns a multipolygon object consisting of the given polygons."}],"fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"multiPolygonWithPolygons:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"multiPolygonWithPolygons:","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"multiPolygonWithPolygons:","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon\/multiPolygonWithPolygons:","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMultiPolygon":{"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon","type":"topic","title":"MLNMultiPolygon","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmultipolygon","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNMultiPolygon"}],"role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMultiPolygon","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object represents a shape consisting of one or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"polygons that do not overlap. For example, you could use a multipolygon shape"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to represent the body of land that consists of an island surrounded by an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"atoll: the inner island would be one "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNPolygon","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object, while the surrounding"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"atoll would be another. You could also use a multipolygon shape to represent a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"group of disconnected but related buildings."}]}}}